race.comment: GRID GIRL (7) brings strong metro form to resumption and Nash Rawiller is a key jockey engagement. Proven fresh and won her most recent Flemington jumpout. Has the ability and looks ready to go. BLAZING HARRY (1) resumed this trip at Caulfield drawn wide and needed the outing. He's right up to winning this and jumps from a low gate today. Expect sharp improvement. ROGUE ROCKER (2) enjoys the sting out of the track and gets that today. He's proving hard to catch, but his best would see him right in the finish. MISO (4) always puts in and handles heavy tracks. He's well seasoned for a tough slog.
